            <description><![CDATA[到点儿！动起！<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[666]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/6c/2022_666_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%AE%9E%E7%94%A8%E6%89%8B%E8%87%82%E7%87%83%E8%84%82%E6%93%8D%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%AE%9E%E7%94%A8%E6%89%8B%E8%87%82%E7%87%83%E8%84%82%E6%93%8D%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#实用手臂燃脂操#</span></a>，胳膊线条不好看？试试练这3个动作：①原地摆臂；②背部击掌；③贴耳肘屈伸。不仅可以练习到手臂前侧、后侧的肌肉群，还能燃烧手臂脂肪，美化手臂线条。每天抽出3分钟，让胳膊线条变好看👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>  <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4933229568786480" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">CCTV生活圈的微博视频</span></a> <br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/orj480/713e54f1ly1hgrqryoclyj20zk0k0417.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/r58AjD0Slx087HiyxHzq0104120263I30E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1691975324&amp;ssig=MRGj948PiT&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/3zx2rt7hlx087HixiFsA01041200WAFi0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1691975324&amp;ssig=bUVr2ixi%2BN&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/6bbuhM8Mlx087Hix2WLu01041200yX9I0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1691975324&amp;ssig=y3F6jLD%2B