            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E4%B8%AD%E5%93%AA%E4%BA%9B%E5%8A%A8%E4%BD%9C%E4%BC%9A%E7%BB%99%E5%8D%8A%E6%9C%88%E6%9D%BF%E5%B8%A6%E6%9D%A5%E5%8E%8B%E5%8A%9B%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E4%B8%AD%E5%93%AA%E4%BA%9B%E5%8A%A8%E4%BD%9C%E4%BC%9A%E7%BB%99%E5%8D%8A%E6%9C%88%E6%9D%BF%E5%B8%A6%E6%9D%A5%E5%8E%8B%E5%8A%9B%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#生活中哪些动作会给半月板带来压力#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[吃惊]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chijing-59b444adb6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】半月板位于膝关节内部，是具有弹性的纤维软骨垫，可起到缓冲两骨撞击、吸收震荡、增加润滑、减少摩擦等作用，有助于膝关节运动功能正常运行。半月板一旦损伤，很难自我修复。日常生活中，哪些动作会给半月板带来压力？戳视频，看<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E5%A7%BF%E5%8A%BF%E4%B8%8B%E8%86%9D%E5%85%B3%E8%8A%82%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%97%E5%8A%9B%E5%80%BC%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E5%A7%BF%E5%8A%BF%E4%B8%8B%E8%86%9D%E5%85%B3%E8%8A%82%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%97%E5%8A%9B%E5%80%BC%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#不同姿势下膝关节的受力值#</span></a>👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>   <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4933262905376779" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视一套的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/orj480/78ad4dbbly1hgruj6s64mj20zk0k0tad.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/R9DEwGRulx087HraJTJK01041200BAeh0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1691975324&amp;ssig=5yguE0m44p&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/a7rqRzh1lx087Hr9ewxy01041200gyAv0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1691975324&amp;ssig=H9qwOi3RZo&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/5B6RaN4Flx087Hr8Y1YI01041200a1t80E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1691975324&amp;ssig=HfgOY7DKIU&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4933262905376779&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
